Anybody have the same issue with terminator?</description><pubDate>Mon, 14 Jul 2014 09:03:32 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/4233/when-terminator-change-to-floating-window-can-only-see-titlebar/</guid></item><item><title>Comment by cee for &lt;p&gt;I have a problem with terminator terminal while working on i3. When I make the terminator window floating, the geometry size becomes so small that I can only see the titlebar. I tried changing the size within terminator's config but without success. I then tried in the i3 config &lt;code&gt;floating_minimum_size 475 x 550&lt;/code&gt; but the problem persists.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Anybody have the same issue with terminator?&lt;/p&gt;
</title><link>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/4233/when-terminator-change-to-floating-window-can-only-see-titlebar/?comment=4236#comment-4236</link><description>Just checked. Same problem here. uname-r: 3.15.5-1-ARCH, i3: v4.8, terminator: 0.97</description><pubDate>Mon, 14 Jul 2014 10:02:46 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/4233/when-terminator-change-to-floating-window-can-only-see-titlebar/?comment=4236#comment-4236</guid></item><item><title>Answer by cee for &lt;p&gt;I have a problem with terminator terminal while working on i3. When I make the terminator window floating, the geometry size becomes so small that I can only see the titlebar. I tried changing the size within terminator's config but without success. I then tried in the i3 config &lt;code&gt;floating_minimum_size 475 x 550&lt;/code&gt; but the problem persists.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Anybody have the same issue with terminator?&lt;/p&gt;
